        "kind": "mistake",
        "front": "设函数y=y(x)由方程x e^{f(y)} = c imes ext{ln}2确定,其中f具有二阶导数,且f'≠1,求 rac{d^2 y}{dx^2}。",
        "back": "首先对原方程两边取对数: \\ln x + f(y) = ext{ln}(c imes ext{ln}2) 对x求导得: \\frac{1}{x} + f'(y)y' = 0 \\Rightarrow y' = -\\frac{1}{xf'(y)} 对y'再次求导得: \\frac{d^2 y}{dx^2} = \\frac{f''(y)y'^2 - f'(y)y''}{x^2(1 - f'(y))} 将y'代入上式并化简得: \\frac{d^2 y}{dx^2} = \\frac{f''(y) - (1 - f'(y))^2}{x^2(1 - f'(y))^2}",
